<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<title>Signin</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
<script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/jquery.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/valid.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
	<header>
		<nav id="nav">
			<ul>
				<li><a title="主页" href="/">主页</a></li>
				<% if(locals.user){ %>
				<li><a title="登出" href="/logout" >退出</a></li>
				<% } else { %>
				<li><a title="登录" href="/login" >登录</a></li>
				<li><a title="注册" href="/regist" >注册</a></li>
				<% } %>
			</ul>
		</nav>
	</header>
	<h1><%= title %></h1>
	<hr>
	<div class="top">
		<figure> <img src="/images/001.png" alt = "天空图">
			<figcaption><strong>不曾起舞的日子，都是对生命的辜负</strong>日子就像永不停息的流水，不停地往前。不敢停下，停下就有变为死水的可能。不是不能停，恰恰是不敢停。这时候，勇气是多么高贵难以触碰的东西。仰望苍穹，思索的尽是未来。梦幻的东西令人向往，未知的事物总有极端的两面性，美好与阴暗。</figcaption>
		</figure>
	</div>
	<p>
		<% if (locals.success) { %>
		<div class="err"><%= locals.success %></div>
		<% } %>
		<% if (locals.error) { %>
		<div class="err"><%= locals.error %> </div>
		<% } %>
		<div id="container">
			<div id="show"></div>
		</div>
	</p>
</body>
</html>